## Database: SQLite → PostgreSQL Migration

### Schema differences

| SQLite | PostgreSQL |
|--------|-----------|
| INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT | BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY |
| datetime('now') | NOW() |
| TEXT for dates | TIMESTAMP |
| 0/1 for boolean | BOOLEAN |
| json.loads() on TEXT | JSONB type |

### Migration strategy
  1. Render PostgreSQL provision karo
  2. Seed command (python -m api.main seed) PostgreSQL pe chalega
  3. Daily data migrate karne ka script likho
  4. Switch DATABASE_URL → postgresql://... restart

